OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FThe government has announced it will
OL,10,Finvest #350 million in changes to
OL,11,Faffordable housing - an action which
OL,12,Fhousing and homelessness charity
OL,13,FShelter has described as "a start".
