OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,FUp to 2,800 extra homes will be built
OL,7,Fthrough a #300 million boost to the
OL,8,FAffordable Homes Programme, with half
OL,9,Fof the homes for social rent, and more
OL,10,Fthan 250 additional council homes
OL,11,Fthrough a #50 million boost to the
OL,12,FLocal Authority Housing Fund to
OL,13,Fprovide homes for those in need of
OL,14,Fbetter-quality temporary
OL,15,Faccommodation, the government said.
OL,17,FShelter has previously recommended
OL,18,Fthat 90,000 new homes are needed each
OL,19,Fyear in order to address the current
OL,20,Fhousing crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
