OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,F"It's definitely a lot less than what
OL,7,Fis actually needed, that's for sure,"
OL,8,FShelter CEO Polly Neate told ITV News
OL,9,Fin response to the announcement.
OL,11,F"It's something to build on though,
OL,12,Fand I think what it does show is that
OL,13,Fthe government is actually serious
OL,14,Fabout specifically committing to a set
OL,15,Fnumber of social homes ... This is
OL,16,Fjust a small stepping stone to get to
OL,17,Fthat," she said.
