OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDeputy Prime Minister and Housing
OL,12,FSecretary Angela Rayner previously
OL,13,Fpromised the Labour government would
OL,14,Fdeliver the "biggest boost to
OL,15,Faffordable housing for a generation"
OL,16,Fin the form of 1.5 million new homes
OL,17,Fduring this parliament.
OL,19,F"We will meet that target because we
OL,20,Fcan't afford not to," Rayner said.
