OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,F"We have 1.3 million people waiting on
OL,7,Fhousing waiting lists. There isn't a
OL,8,Fperson listening to this ... that will
OL,9,Fnot know somebody who is desperate to
OL,10,Fget on the housing ladder.
OL,12,F"So therefore we're determined to turn
OL,13,Fthat tide," she added.
OL,15,FLabour's latest announcement also
OL,16,Fincluded plans to help "the most
OL,17,Fvulnerable in society" with a
OL,18,F"crackdown on exploitative behaviour
OL,19,Fby rogue and criminal supported
OL,20,Fhousing landlords".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
