OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,F"(They) are costing the taxpayer by
OL,7,Fclaiming uncapped housing benefit in
OL,8,Freturn for providing squalid homes for
OL,9,Fthe most vulnerable, leaving them
OL,10,Fwithout the care or support they
OL,11,Fneed," it said in a statement.
OL,13,FMs Neate said it was "great to see"
OL,14,Fthose changes, but added that the
OL,15,Fproblem only exists because of the
OL,16,Flack of homes for people on low
OL,17,Fincomes.
OL,19,F"It does all double back to the need
OL,20,Fto see a real serious commitment to
OL,21,Fbuilding social housing," she said.
