OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,FThe next big test for Labour's
OL,7,Fcommitments on housing - and other
OL,8,Fspending pledges it made on winning
OL,9,Fthe election - will be the spending
OL,10,Freview, which is set to be published
OL,11,Fin late spring.
OL,13,FAs for what Shelter is hoping to see,
OL,14,Fthe charity's CEO was very clear.
OL,16,F"We're hoping to see a commitment to
OL,17,Fbuilding up, by the end of the
OL,18,Fparliament, to be delivering 90,000
OL,19,Fnew social homes a year," Ms Neate
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
