OL,3,CGovernment announces #350 million for
OL,4,Caffordable and social homes
OL,6,F"The only way to end homelessness is
OL,7,Fto build homes that people on low
OL,8,Fincomes can actually afford to rent,
OL,9,Fand at the moment, we simply, as a
OL,10,Fcountry, we are not providing homes
OL,11,Fthat people on low incomes can afford.
OL,13,F"This is a start. This is homes that
OL,14,Fclearly are specifically aimed at
OL,15,Fthose people. We need to see a lot
OL,16,Fmore of it."
